en_98047_0	A representative group of 11 Division troops, headed by their General Officer Commanding, Major General W.G.H.A Senarath Bandara, recently visited the 'Abimansala - 3' at Pangolla on account of the 70th Army Anniversary Day and interacted with those inmates.
en_98047_1	Afterwards, the visiting GOC 11 Division inquired into the daily routine of those War Heroes and other measures being adopted to look after them.
en_98047_2	He, together with a couple of Officers, spoke to those inmates and shared a few thoughts with them before some gift parcels were offered to them.
en_98047_3	He also discussed matters of relevance with the staff at 'Abimansala - 3' Pangolla and shared some valuable thoughts with them.
